      "message": "1. Generally sgtm, but I don\u0027t know if users would understand what is \"inv-level\". Many of them don\u0027t know what invocation is\n2. subsection - meaning sub-node of the Artifacts node? This sounds like more clicking/clutter\n3. Generally sgtm, but sounds more complicated than (1) because we have two nodes.\n\nRe problem (1): I think we have to provide some tooltip with an explanation. It would cover the typical use case: all logs from the same swarming task, since users know what swarming task is.\n\nso I prefer (1) with a tooltip,\n\nalso consider a variation of (1) where instead of \"inv-level\" we display some icon that users will get used to. The rationale is once they are used to, \"inv-level\" provides the same amount of information as a small icon, but with more letters.",
